User Module - API,s

User Registration 

API URL: localhost:8080/user/add
Method : POST
Required Field:name,email,password
Access Type:Public 

Note: Bcrypt JS 

User Login 
API URL: localhost:8080/user/login
Method : POST
Required Field:email,password
Access Type:Public 

Note: JWT


Get User 
API URL: localhost:8080/user/
Method : GET
Required Field:Token - reading token from browser local storage
Access Type:Public 


Install Required Dependencies:
npm i express morgan mongoose dotenv
